ight=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2002700/extras/0815cd6b7c2d5c53144eeed8b1738fb9.webm?t=1698154620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2002700/extras/0815cd6b7c2d5c53144eeed8b1738fb9.mp4?t=1698154620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY RESOURCES</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Support for screens Ultra Wide (21:9)</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 30 levels.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Innovative instruction system.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Follow this intriguing dialogue between creation and creator.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Think and solve amazing puzzles with different mechanics.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2002700/extras/c38535e636896ec6f493ddb2d447a076.poster.avif?t=1698154620\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2002700/extras/c38535e636896ec6f493ddb2d447a076.webm?t=1698154620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2002700/extras/c38535e636896ec6f493ddb2d447a076.mp4?t=1698154620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Watch out for the laser beams!!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2002700/extras/169acaf789067efee8c87da5ed6e7e67.poster.avif?t=1698154620\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2002700/extras/169acaf789067efee8c87da5ed6e7e67.webm?t=1698154620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2002700/extras/169ac